{"tid":1040313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】港鐵扶手電梯無故伸出鐵片 割傷大量乘客","createTime":"2019-02-28T04:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T04:32:15.000Z","uid":117200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b411dea918dc256b7f22618e288a3fb33af04da1","tid":1040313,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190228/large/1551322006_c6b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190228%2Flarge%2F1551322006_c6b4.jpg&h=8cf71d11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上9時左右，牛頭角港鐵站扶手電梯發生意外，3男6女受傷，部份傷者被扶到大堂等候治理，3部救護車先後將他們送院。傷者主要是小腿被割傷，當中有女乘客的牛仔褲也被割爛。<br />\n部份傷者經急症室醫生包紮敷治後出院，其中一名女傷者說：「有條鐵片勾咗出嚟，刮到小腿位置上5吋下5吋。」她表示不知道該鐵片何以會勾出，幸當時情況不算混亂，沒有人絆倒，事後港鐵職員按停扶手電梯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190228/large/1551318221_c786.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190228%2Flarge%2F1551318221_c786.jpg&h=55de2876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者在現場所見，一部下行扶手電梯封閉，在接近地面右手邊位置，一塊鐵片狀的配件翻出，消防員及警員等在場檢視。<br />\n在場的港鐵職員向警員解說稱，不知鐵片如何翻出，事發時很多乘客搭乘扶手電梯，「可能太多人落嚟，一路都停唔到，扶手梯一直落緊，乘客盡量企埋一邊，向呢邊（左邊）企，唔企嗰邊。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190228/large/1551318221_e208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190228%2Flarge%2F1551318221_e208.jpg&h=f510995b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警員問是否有手拉車之類物體勾出鐵片，職員說：「冇，全部都係人，冇車仔。」<br />\n有讀者表示，今早9時前到達牛頭角站時，月台往大堂的扶手電梯只有一部開動，多人排隊等候，相當擠迫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190228/large/1551318504_6f3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190228%2Flarge%2F1551318504_6f3f.jpg&h=bad2a1d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵稱，上午9點左右，觀塘綫牛頭角站一條由月台往大堂的扶手電梯，右側旁板有一支固定旁板的部件伸出，觸及扶手電梯上乘客的腳部，車站職員到場即時停止該扶手梯運作。現場有9名乘客腳部受傷，由救護車送院治理，車站方面已安排職員到醫院探望傷者，表達慰問。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190228/large/1551321113_ef5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190228%2Flarge%2F1551321113_ef5f.jpg&h=cc75b461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車站亦已通知扶手電梯承辦商到場檢查及了解事故原因，觀塘綫列車服務不受影響。<br />\n另外，牛頭角站有3條扶手電梯，事發前兩條下行、一條上行，但其中一條下行扶手電梯因維修暫停使用。"},{"pid":"93bd34e68a0b6e43ed535e6f80b32a60b49a9ea0","tid":1040313,"uid":115347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"價照加 野照壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c51451b30a90972358aa3f9adcdac8a81faaedb","tid":1040313,"uid":67325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93bd34e68a0b6e43ed535e6f80b32a60b49a9ea0","tid":1040313,"uid":115347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"價照加 野照壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:22:49.000Z","msg":"咁要再加價嚟維修喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95b8d53bd5cc6beb96ffa108596ebc81133fba0","tid":1040313,"uid":214016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:23:29.000Z","msg":"有無錢賠？？"},{"pid":"fd86c338c00d7b1772f14b31d7b2bd963c18b952","tid":1040313,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:24:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XqFNEpRNN3Y&amp;has_verified=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXqFNEpRNN3Y%26has_verified%3D1&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=10acfac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XqFNEpRNN3Y&amp;has_verifie